495
00:29:50,289 --> 00:29:52,719
but that became the key location
for that sequence.

496
00:29:53,125 --> 00:29:55,935
We realized, once we knew that Oogway

497
00:29:56,395 --> 00:29:59,615
was going to have this
very beautiful death scene,

498
00:30:00,132 --> 00:30:03,232
that we had to introduce
the peach tree earlier.

