00:35:48,480 --> 00:35:50,410
There was a great gag
where Po was asleep.

605
00:35:50,749 --> 00:35:54,499
He had been trying to do splits all
night, and ended up falling asleep,

606
00:35:55,086 --> 00:35:58,185
