00:36:08,900 --> 00:36:11,890
This is where it's dawning on him

611
00:36:12,370 --> 00:36:13,830
how much of a fan this guy is.

612
00:36:14,105 --> 00:36:15,395
He's not going to quit.

613
00:36:15,640 --> 00:36:18,270
He keeps trying to turn up the heat,
to scare him away,

614
00:36:18,710 --> 00:36:22,280
trying to raise the intensity
of his attack on Po.

615
00:36:23,915 --> 00:36:27,425
He can't do it overtly, because that
would be going against Oogway's wishes.

616
00:36:27,986 --> 00:36:30,826
And this sequence is all about Shifu
turning up the heat

