01:09:17,420 --> 01:09:18,560
giving Po the secret.

1180
01:09:18,787 --> 01:09:22,447
It's brilliantly played by James Hong.
James did a magical job

1181
01:09:23,026 --> 01:09:26,505
with the delivery of these lines,
making them warm and heartfelt

1182
01:09:27,063 --> 01:09:29,752
and sympathetic.

